                        **org/kawanfw/file/api/server/**,
        	
        				**org/kawanfw/sql/WebServer.class
        				**org/kawanfw/sql/tomcat/**,
                        **org/kawanfw/sql/servlet/**, 
                        **org/kawanfw/sql/api/server/**,
